Liikanen Says Governments Must Brace for Bank Aid, Reuters Says

-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 
2011-10-13T08:38:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/liikanen-says-governments-must-brace-for-bank-aid-reuters-says.html
Europe ’s governments must “be
ready” to shore up the region’s banks if they cannot raise the
required capital from investors, European Central Bank council
member  Erkki Liikanen  said today, Reuters reported. Banks that
aren’t solvent should be restructured, he said according to
